main event: An object was observed in Albuquerque, New Mexico at around 7:15 pm on 5 March 1965, described as erratically moving like a bird or searchlight.
interesting points: The object was seen through a window by a witness,Its size and shape could not be determined,The sighting lasted approximately one minute,The object displayed erratic movement up and down as well as side to side,The report suggested the probable cause of the sighting could be aircraft.
sighted object: an object resembling a bird or searchlight
